voids%20them.%20Here%20are%20her%203%20favorite%20healthy%2C%20quick%20snacks.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image.%20Dates%20filled%20with%20nut%20butter%20and%20pistachios%20on%20the%20left.%20Linia%20Patel%20smiling%2C%20wearing%20a%20white%20blouse%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66abaebd1a227600e6337e2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELinia%20Patel%20leans%20on%20whole%20foods%20to%20avoid%20ultra-processed%20snacks.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%2FLinia%20Patel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUltra-processed%20foods%20have%20been%20linked%20to%20health%20problems%2C%20including%20obesity%20and%20depression.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESnacks%20make%20up%2025%25%20of%20US%20calorie%20intake%20and%20people%20tend%20to%20choose%20UPFs%20because%20they're%20convenient.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20dietitian%20shared%20her%20go-to%20minimally%20processed%20snacks%20that%20stop%20her%20from%20reaching%20for%20UPFs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20dietitian%20whose%20research%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplant-based-upf-processed-linked-heart-disease-death-study-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20harms%20of%20ultra-processed%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20led%20her%20to%20eat%20fewer%20of%20them%20shared%20her%20three%20favorite%20quick%2C%20minimally%20processed%20snacks%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinia%20Patel%2C%20who%20is%20based%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Milan%2C%20Italy%2C%20said%20people%20generally%20eat%20%26quot%3Bfar%20too%20many%26quot%3B%20UPFs.%20Such%20products%20tend%20to%20be%20ultra-palatable%20thanks%20to%20their%20high%20salt%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20fat%20content%2C%20but%20low%20in%20nutrients%20and%20fiber%2C%20and%2C%20crucially%2C%20shelf-stable%2C%20and%20convenient.%20Eating%20lots%20of%20%3Ca%