e%20to%20sell%20beachfront%20property%20is%20yesterday%2C%20a%20bubble-spotting%20analyst%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReal-estate%20researcher%20David%20Burt%2C%20who's%20best%20known%20for%20seeing%20the%20danger%20in%20subprime%20mortgages%20before%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-housing-market-climate-change-outlook-prediction-floods-burt-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalling%20for%20another%20housing%20market%20crash%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20unlike%202008%2C%20this%20downturn%20will%20be%20narrower%20in%20scope%20and%20will%20be%20largely%20caused%20by%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20steadily%20rising%20global%20temperatures%20and%20their%20effects%20are%20increasingly%20hard%20to%20ignore%2C%20Burt%20believes%20they're%20not%20yet%20factored%20into%20property%20values.%20He%20expects%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-beryl-caribbean-storm-weather-jamaica-record-category-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esevere%20storms%20like%20hurricanes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20become%20more%20common%20and%20more%20intense%20due%20to%20warmer%20weather%2C%20which%20will%20cause%20insurance%20premiums%20to%20soar%20%E2%80%94%20thereby%20reducing%20what%20buyers%20will%20pay%20for%20homes%20by%20up%20to%2060%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Burt's%20mind%2C%20there's%20no%20solution%20for%20this%20coming%20calamity.%20Flood%20insurance%20costs%20will%20skyrocket%20since%20they're%20severely%20underpriced%20to%20climate%20risk%2C%20his%20research%20indicates.%20And%20if%20those%20premiums%20were%20artificially%20capped%2C%20insurers%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20financially%20viable%20and%20could%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20expect%20these%20problems%20to%20be%20solved%20by%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Burt%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20government%20cannot%20change%20the%20laws%20of%20phy