ng%20Jena%20as%20a%20baby%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20plan%20would%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20we%20sold%20our%20house%2C%20bought%20an%20RV%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhippest-us-cities-2017-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Vancouver%2C%20Washington%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We've%20been%20very%20fortunate%20to%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20with%20the%20kids.%20It's%20been%20great%2C%20though%20there%20have%20been%20challenges.%20It%20could%20have%20been%20disastrous%20for%20us%20had%20we%20not%20had%20such%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f8c6309-4984-48c1-8d4b-e3722510b978%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20try%20to%20pay%20for%20as%20much%20as%20they%20allow%20me%20to%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERelationships%20are%20challenging.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-decor-tips-moving-in-husband-wife-house-blended-family-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoving%20into%20a%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20owned%20by%20your%20adult%20children%20is%20a%20role%20reversal%20that%20some%20may%20have%20difficulty%20adjusting%20to.%20It's%20not%20your%20house%3B%20you%20are%20no%20longer%20the%20leader%3B%20you're%20a%20follower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-stress-bankruptcies-foreclosures-car-repossesssions-economy-confidence-debt-payment-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoney%20can%20be%20a%20major%20stress%3C%2Fa%3E%20point%20in%20any%20relationship%2C%20and%20adding%20additional%20people%20to%20a%20household%20comes%20with%20added%20costs.%20My%20son%20refuses%20to%20accept%20rent%20from%20me%20and%20won't%20let%20me%20pay%20any%20of%20the%20bills%2C%20so%20we%20take%20it%20out%20in%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20household%20chores%2C%20even%20yard%20work.%20Once%20a%20week%2C%20we%20do%20the%20grocery%20shopping%20or%20pay%20for%20a%20Costco%20run.%20On%20Thursdays%2C%20I'll%20get%20takeout%2C%20or%20we'll%20all%20go%20to%20a%20restaurant%2C%20my%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20bought%20a%20fixer-upper%20house%2C%20and%20there%20is%20always%20some%20project%20underway%20that%20we%20are%20helping%20with.%20I%20thought%20that%20being%20retired%20would%20be%20more%20relaxing%2C%20but%20I%20regularly%20find%20myself%20hanging%20drywall%2C%20painting%2C%20putting%20in%20new%20fencing%2C%20or%20installing%20flooring.%20The%20work%20we%20do%20not%20only%20saves%20the%20kids%20money%20but%20also%20gives%20them%20more%20time%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ef8e353-565a-41b5-8d9c-d2f81c78e020%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20provide%20childcare%20for%20them%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJena%20is%20our%20granddaughter%2C%20and%20we%20take%20care%20of%20her%20because%20we%20love%20her%2C%20not%20because%20it%20is%20a%20chore%20or%20some%20way%20to%20offset%20expenses.%20It's%20fun%20being%20with%20her%2C%20going%20on%20walks%20to%20the%20park%20or%20the%20corner%20store%20to%20get%20ice%20cream%2C%20or%20playing%20in%20her%20blow-up%20pool%20in%20the%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20a%20way%20to%20help%20the%20kids%20out.%20They%20can%20go%20out%20on%20a%20dinner%20date%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20her.%20Sometimes%2C%20they'll%20go%20to%20a%20concert%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20get%20back%20until%20after%20Jena's%20asleep.%20She%20says%20night-night%20to%20mommy%20and%20daddy%2C%20gives%20them%20big%20hugs%2C%20and%20waves%20to%20them%20out%20the%20window.%20Then%2C%20we%20have%20a%20yummy%20dinner%20and%20a%20fun%20evening%20before%20bedtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a46fa0b-1440-46e2-a9db-5efa3277dc0a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEveryone%20has%20their%20own%20space%20so%20we%20can%20have%20boundaries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20are%20staying%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20we%20are%20in%20the%20RV.%20We%20come%20over%20a%20few%20times%20during%20the%20day%2C%20and%20for%20family%20dinners%2C%20and%20Jena%20will%20come%20over%20and%20visit%20us.%20But%20we%20have%20our%20own%20space%20so%20everyone%20can%20have%20some%20separate%20time.%20If%20they%20have%20friends%20over%2C%20we%20make%20ourselves%20scarce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20our%20house%2C%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20ask%20permission.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%20other%20adults%20to%20contend%20with%2C%20and%20there%20can%20be%20clashes.%20You've%20got%20to%20respect%20each%20other's%20boundaries%2C%20especially%20with%20grandkids.%20When%20you%20live%20in%20a%20multi-generational%20house%2C%20you're%20not%20a%20visiting%20grandparent%3B%20you're%20often%20acting%20as%20a%20parent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kids%20also%20need%20to%20recognize%20that%20although%20it's%20fun%20being%20around%20the%20grandkids%2C%20sometimes%20Gigi%20and%20Papa%20need%20a%20break.%20Chasing%20a%203-year-old%20around%20can%20really%20take%20it%20out%20of%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22731a2e84-02a6-4750-b31b-24699b3aef6a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20all%20have%20to%20be%20on%20the%20same%20page%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20essential%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20everyone%20is%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20Even%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20making%20dinner%20needs%20to%20be%20discussed.%20We%20don't%20just%20go%20over%20and%20start%20cooking%20food%20or%20even%20fixing%20lunch%20for%20Jena%20without%20asking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20tool%20we%20use%20is%20an%20erasable%20calendar%20on%20the%20kids'%20fridge.%20Play%20dates%2C%20doctor%20appointments%2C%20yoga%20classes%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20goes%20on%20the%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20house%20with%20my%20mom%20and%20grandparents.%20Our%20son%20lived%20with%20us%20during%20college%2C%20and%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20lived%20with%20us%20for%20over%20a%20year%20before%20and%20after%20their%20wedding.%20This%20new%20life%20just%20seems%20normal%20and%20is%20mutually%