l.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20urged%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20not%20to%20ignore%20the%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20Demands%20CBI%20Enquiry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly%20and%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leader%2C%20has%20demanded%20a%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20inquiry%20into%20the%20death%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20body%20of%20the%20second-year%20postgraduate%20student%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%2C%20found%20dead%20inside%20the%20Seminar%20Hall%20on%20the%203rd%20floor%20of%20the%20emergency%20building%20under%20mysterious%20circumstances%2C%20reportedly%20had%20injury%20marks.%20Unconfirmed%20reports%20suggest%20signs%20of%20strangulation%20and%20traces%20of%20seminal%20fluid.%20This%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20murder%2C%20possibly%20involving%20rape.%20The%20case%20should%20be%20immediately%20transferred%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticizing%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20addressing%20the%20issue%20seriously%2C%20the%20State%20Government%20has%20formed%20an%2011-member%20inquiry%20committee%2C%20which%20bizarrely%20includes%20some%20interns.%20It%20seems%20the%20government%20is%20either%20trying%20to%20cover%20up%20its%20negligence%20or%20is%20not%20taking%20this%20matter%20seriously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%20second-year%20Postgraduate%20Student%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%2C%20who%20was%20found%20dead%20inside%20the%20Seminar%20Hall%20on%20the%203rd%20floor%20of%20the%20emergency%20building%20inside%20the%20campus%20under%20mysterious%20circ