r%20comments%20were%20%E2%80%9Cmisinterpreted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20explained%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20she%20said%20were%20not%20%26quot%3Balways%20necessarily%20about%20the%20current%20team%20because%20I%20love%20and%20support%20all%20the%20girls%20that%20made%20it%20and%20I'm%20so%20proud%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20more%20about%20going%20back%20into%20my%20own%20gym%2C%20just%20the%20work%20ethic%20is%20different%20compared%20to%20when%20we%20were%20doing%20gymnastics%20in%20the%20M%C3%A1rta%20era%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20sticking%20up%20for%20M%C3%A1rta%20or%20saying%20what%20she%20did%20was%20good%2C%20I'm%20just%20saying%20it%20was%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20she%20apologised%20to%20the%20current%20team%20and%20said%20she%20was%20%E2%80%9Cseriously%20so%20happy%20for%20them%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20People%20magazine%20last%20month%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUpon%20reflection%20I%20was%20comparing%20the%20'Marta%20Era'%20to%20the%20current%20era.%20I%20am%20coming%20to%20terms%20that%20I%20have%20not%20fully%20dealt%20with%20the%20emotional%20and%20verbal%20abuse%20I%20endured%20under%20Marta%20that%20perhaps%20led%20to%20my%20hurtful%20comments.%20I%20take%20full%20responsibility%20for%20what%20I%20said%20and%20I%20deeply%20apologise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBiles%20takes%20a%20jibe%20at%20Skinner%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Team%20USA%20won%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20team%20all-around%20competition%20at%20the%202024%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20Biles%20shared%20photographs%20of%20herself%20with%20other%20teammates%20and%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20talent%2C%20lazy%2C%20olympic%20champions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https