Ftv%2Fnews%2Fdaredevil-born-again-footage-release-date-1235363615%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDid%20Not%20Sleep%20At%20All...%26quot%3B%3A%20Aman%20Reveals%20Tough%20Journey%20To%20Olympics%20Bronze%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAman%20Sehrawat%20scripted%20history%20by%20becoming%20India's%20youngest%20ever%20medalist%20at%20the%20Olympics%20as%20he%20claimed%20bronze%20in%20the%2057kg%20freestyle%20wrestling%20event%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%20Aman%20defeated%C2%A0Puerto%20Rico's%20Darian%20Cruz%20in%20the%20bronze%20medal%20match%20on%20Friday%20to%20clinch%20India's%20first%20medal%20in%20wrestling%20at%20this%20year's%20Olympics.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Aman%20opened%20up%20about%20what%20the%20medal%20meant%20for%20him%20and%20said%20that%20although%20his%20dream%20was%20to%20win%20the%20gold%2C%20this%20medal%20will%20motivate%20him%20to%20perform%20well%20in%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20with%20the%20dream%20of%20winning%20a%20medal%20at%20the%20Olympics.%20Wanted%20to%20win%20gold%20but%20everything%20happens%20for%20one's%20good.%20Next%20time%2C%20I%20will%20be%20better%20prepared.%20This%20was%20a%20big%20boost%20for%20me%20and%20I%20have%20the%20belief%20now%20that%20I%20will%20surely%20do%20well%20in%20the%202028%20Olympics%2C%26quot%3B%20Aman%20told%20NDTV%20after%20the%20bronze%20medal%20triumph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20loss%20to%C2%A0Japan's%20Rei%20Higuchi%20in%20the%20semifinals%2C%20Aman%20was%20overweight%20and%20he%20needed%20to%20get%20back%20into%20the%20permissible%20limit%20before%20the%20weigh-in.%20The%20wrestler%20said%20that%20they%20worked%20overnight%20on%20his%20weight%20and%20he%20did%20not%20sleep%20at%20all%20as%20his%20coaches%20put%20him%20through%20multiple%20training%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20a%20lot%20to%20lose%20that%20weight.%20Once%20the%20bout%20ended%2C%20I%20practiced%20for%20two%20hours.%20Then%20at%20around%201am%2C%20I%20trained%20at%20the%20gym.%20By%203%2C%20I%20was%20somewhat%20done.%20But%20I%20did%20not%20sleep%20at%20all.%20The%20main%20target%20was%20to%20get%20the%20weight%20within%20the%20permissible%20limit.%20Did%20not%20sleep%20at%20all%20before%20the%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20also%20qualified%20for%20the%2050kg%20wrestling%20final%20but%20she%20was%20disqualified%20from%20the%20gold%20medal%20match%20for%20being%20overweight.%20After%20the%20decision%20was%20challenged%C2%A0in%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS)%2C%20the%20hearing%20has%20concluded%20and%20a%20decision%20is%20expected%20by%20Sunday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723262700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fp3p13gf_aman-sehrawat_625x300_10_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fdid-not-sleep-at-all-aman-sehrawat-on-getting-ready-for-paris-olympics-2024-wrestling-bronze-bout-6305186%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aman%20Sehrawat%20scripted%20history%20by%20becoming%20India's%20youngest%20even%20medalist%20at%20the%20Olympics%20as%20he%20claimed%20bronze%20in%20the%2057kg%20freestyle%20wrestling%20event%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fdid-not-sleep-at-all-aman-sehrawat-on-getting-ready-for-paris-olympics-2024-wrestling-bronze-bout-6305186%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20Antim%20Factor%20Really%20Force%20Vinesh%20To%20Compete%20In%2050kg%20-%20A%20Fact-Check%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20arrived%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20her%20biggest%20challenge%20wasn't%20to%20compete%20against%20an%20astounding%20list%20of%20wrestlers%20but%20to%20manage%20her%20weight%20as%20she%20was%20competing%20in%20the%2050kg%20category%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%2053kg%20category%20she%20was%20more%20comfortable%20in.%20Months%20before%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20were%20to%20start%20in%20Paris%2C%20Vinesh%20tried%20to%20do%20her%20best%20and%20fetch%20the%20lone%2053kg%20spot%2C%20but%20Antim%20Panghal%2C%20a%202023%20World%20Championship%20bronze%20medallist%20in%20the%20weight%20category%2C%20had%20won%20slot%20in%20this%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAntim%20facing%20a%200-10%20elimination%20in%20the%20Round%20of%2016%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%20As%20the%20entire%20Indi%20stares%20at%20the%20nature%20of%20affairs%20that%20unfolded%20in%20the%20Paris%20Games%2C%20many%20wonder%20if%20Vinesh%20would've%20fetched%20a%20medal%20by%20competing%20in%20the%2053kg%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20led%20to%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20competing%20in%20the%2050kg%20category%2C%20and%20not%2053kg%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20has%20been%20wrestling%20in%20the%2053kg%20category%20for%20the%20last%20five%20to%20six%C2%A0%20years.%20She%20had%20an%20ACL%20surgery%20in%20August%20last%20year%20which%20ruled%20her%20out%20of%20action%20for%20a%20few%20months.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20Antim%20sealed%20the%20Olympic%20quota%20for%20the%2053kg%20category%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Folympics%2Fparis-2024%2Fnews%2Fparis-olympics-vinesh-phogat-disqualified-wrestling-final-overweight-100-grams-rules-diet-process-training-dreams-crushed%2Farticle68498070.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Vinesh%20wanted%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20still%20manageable%2053kg%20category%20but%20Antim%20Panghal%20had%20already%20claimed%20that%20spot.%20Vinesh%20even%20asked%20the%20federation%20for%20a%20trial%20to%20be%20conducted%2C%20asking%20for%20specific%20dates%2C%20but%20the%20federation%20didn't%20provide%20any%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20About%20The%20Trials%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOA's%20ad-hoc%20committee%20for%20wrestling%20conducted%20trials%20for%20the%20Asian%20Championships%20and%20Asian%20Olympic%20Qualifiers%20in%20March.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20set%20was%20the%20winner%20of%20the%20trial%20woukd%20go%20on%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20Asian%20Olympic%20Qualifiers%20and%20runner-up%20at%20the%20Asian%20Championships.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20decided%20that%20four%20top%20players%20in%20every%20weight%20category%2C%20including%2053kg%20category%2C%20would%20then%20compete%20among%20themselves%20to%20determine%20a%20challenger%20for%20the%20quota-winners%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20Olympic%20spot.%20Antim%20was%20the%20quota%20winner%20in%20the%2053kg%20as%20she%20finished%20with%20a%20bronze%20at%20the%20World%20Championships.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20shooting%2C%20in%20wrestling%2C%20the%20quota%20is%20given%20to%20the%20National%20Olympic%20Committee%20and%20not%20the%20player.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20the%20trials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20trials%2C%20Vinesh%20participated%20in%20two%20weight%20categories%20-%2050%20and%2053kg.%20The%20ad-hoc%20committee%20made%20an%20exception%20and%20allowed%20Vinesh%20to%20compete%20in%20both%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20won%20the%20trials%20in%2050kg%2C%20thus%20earning%20the%20right%20to%20compete%20at%20the%20Asian%20Olympic%20qualifiers%20in%20Bishkek.%20She%20had%20to%20reach%2053kg%20category%20to%20feature%20in%20the%20top%20four%20to%20challenge%20Antim%20at%20a%20later%20date.%20Vinesh%20achieved%20her%20target.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Vinesh%20won%20the%20quota%20in%2050kg%20for%20Paris%202024%20during%20the%20Asian%20Olympic%20Qualifiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20the%20trials%20conducted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20trials%20were%20not%20held%20as%20most%20wrestlers%20who%20won%20the%20quotas%20said%20that%20it%20would%20hamper%20their%20Olympics%20preparation.%20The%20seven-member%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20selection%20committee%20then%20decided%20not%20to%20hold%20the%20trials%20and%20sent%20the%20respective%20quota-winners%20to%20their%20categories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723261980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Foejr8rdo_vinesh-and-antim_625x300_08_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fparis-olympics-did-antim-panghal-factor-really-force-vinesh-phogat-to-compete-in-50kg-a-fact-check-6291222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Paris%20Olympic%20Games%20saw%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20ditch%20her%20usual%2053kg%20category%20and%20compete%20in%20the%2050kg%20category%2C%20which%20proved%20to%20be%20quite%20problematic%20as%20far%20as%20weight%20management%20goes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fparis-olympics-did-antim-panghal-factor-really-force-vinesh-phogat-to-compete-in-50kg-a-fact-check-6291222%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Airstrike%20On%20Gaza%20School%20Kills%20100%2C%20Israel%20Says%20It%20Was%20Hamas%20Command%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGaza's%20civil%20defence%20agency%20said%20Saturday%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20hit%20a%20school%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20killing%2090-100%20people%2C%20while%20the%20Israeli%20military%20said%20it%20had%20struck%20a%20Hamas%20command%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForty%20martyrs%20and%20dozens%20wounded%20after%20the%20Israeli%20bombing%20of%20the%20Al-Taba'een%20school%20in%20the%20Al-Sahaba%20area%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20agency%20spokesman%20Mahmoud%20Basal%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBasal%20described%20the%20incident%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20horrific%20massacre%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20some