zes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-4-1723194511.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ground-mounted%20solar%20panels%20are%20a%20novel%20way%20of%20harnessing%20solar%20energy%20for%20industrial%20operations%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-4-1723194511.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-4-1723194511-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-4-1723194511-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-4-1723194511-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-4-1723194511-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360484%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20ground-mounted%20solar%20panels%20are%20a%20novel%20way%20of%20harnessing%20solar%20energy%20for%20industrial%20operations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Merino%20Industries%20has%20been%20an%20early%20adopter%20of%20solar%20energy%2C%20it%20has%20also%20been%20exploring%20renewable%20energy%20options%20from%20wind%20plants.%20The%20impact%20is%20notable.%20In%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023-24%2C%20only%2018.2%20percent%20of%20their%20energy%20needs%20were%20met%20with%20fossil%20fuels%2C%207.2%20percent%20from%20State%20Electricity%20Boards%20(SEB)%20grids%2C%20and%20massive%2074.6%20percent%20from%20renewable%20sources.%20By%202027%2C%20they%20aim%20to%20exceed%2090%20percent%20from%20non-fossil%20fuel%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20touched%20a%20milestone%20in%20the%202022-23%20period%2C%20ensuring%20that%20100%20percent%20of%20the%20heat%20energy%20required%20(12.64%20Lakh%20GJ)%20at%20the%20Rohad%20and%20Hapur%20factories%20was%20produced%20in-house%20using%20boilers%20and%20secondary%20furnaces%2C%20primarily%20from%20non-fossil%20fuels%20namely%20rice%20husk%20and%20saw%20dust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIncrease%20energy%20efficiency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerino%20Industries%20is%20committed%20to%20achieving%20energy%20efficiency%20in%20every%20operation.%20Less%20energy%20consumption%20should%20yield%20more%20output.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20constantly%20upgrade%20electrical%20tools%2C%20appliances%2C%20and%20machinery%2C%20and%20bring%20in%20improved%20technology%20for%20operations%2C%20utilities%2C%20and%20lighting%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Lohia%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConservation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnergy%20consciousness%20extends%20beyond%20factories%20to%20every%20office%20at%20Merino%20Industries.%20Procuring%20and%20using%20energy-saving%20equipment%2C%20machines%2C%20and%20tools%20is%20key%20to%20conserving%20energy%20from%20the%20start.%20Natural%20light%20is%20promoted%2C%20and%20automatic%20lighting%20systems%20reduce%20manual%20intervention.%20%E2%80%9CConservation%20of%20energy%20is%20achieved%20through%20an%20eco-conscious%20work%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Lohia%20explains%2C%20adding%20that%20automation%20and%20workforce%20education%20encourage%20responsible%20energy%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-6_11zon-1723194810.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20campuses%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20reflect%20sustainable%20eco-friendly%20practices%20in%20every%20corner%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu