%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vermicompost%20beds%20have%20been%20created%20to%20support%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVermicompost%20beds%20have%20been%20created%20to%20support%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20success%20story%20is%20scripted%20in%20how%20over%2075%2C000%20metric%20tons%20of%20GHG%20(greenhouse%20gas)%20or%20tCO2e%20(metric%20tons%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20equivalent)%20emissions%20in%20air%20were%20saved%20in%20the%20reporting%20year%20by%20utilising%20agro-residues%20(biogenic%20fuels)%20instead%20of%20coal%20in%20the%20boilers%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20facilities%20at%20the%20Rohad%20and%20Hapur%20plant%20of%20Merino.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerino%20prides%20itself%20on%20collaborating%20with%20academia%20and%20integrating%20expert%20opinions%20in%20their%20industrial%20processes%2C%20as%20they%20attempt%20to%20align%20with%20sustainable%20goals.%20One%20of%20these%20collaborations%20was%20with%20Visvesvaraya%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(VNIT%2C%20Nagpur).%20The%20latter%20assisted%20Merino%E2%80%99