r%20efficiency%20is%20increased%20following%20some%20retrofitting%20processes.%20A%20similar%20automation%20is%20done%20for%20heating%20and%20cooling%20systems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20motors%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20have%20been%20upgraded%20to%20IE3%20technology%2C%20which%20promises%20premium%20efficiency%20while%20being%20environmentally%20friendly.%20Meanwhile%2C%20through%20the%2010.59%20MW%20solar%20power%20system%2C%20approximately%2012.77%20million%20kWh%20units%20of%20electrical%20energy%20are%20generated%20%E2%80%94%20which%20accounts%20for%20around%2024%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20electrical%20energy%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20features%20of%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20energy%20source%20include%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ea)%20Procurement%20from%20the%20local%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Eb)%20Production%20of%20around%20one%20million%20gigajoules%20of%20energy%20(FY2023-24)%2C%20meeting%20the%20heat%20requirements%20of%20its%20processing%20units%20in%20Hapur%20(Uttar%20Pradesh)%20and%20Rohad%20(Haryana)%20through%20complete%20combustion%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ec)%20Reduction%20of%20GHG%20emissions%20by%20approximately%2095%2C000%20MT%20of%20CO2%20equivalent%2C%20which%20would%20have%20otherwise%20been%20generated%20from%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%20like%20coal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ed)%20Pioneering%20the%20use%20of%20biomass%20since%202005%20and%20turbine%20technology%20in%20Hapur%20which%20extracts%20energy%20in%20electrical%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20creation%20of%20Miyawaki%20Forests%20at%20Hapur%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20Merino%20Industries'%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360498%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20creation%20of%20Miyawaki%20Forests%20at%20Hapur%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20Merino%20Industries%E2%80%99%20commitment%20to%20sustainability.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20roadmap%20has%20guided%20Merino%20Industries%20in%20achieving%20energy%20efficiency.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20company%20has%20expanded%20its%20focus%20to%20water%2C%20air%2C%20and%20soil%2C%20primarily%20relying%20on%20renewable%20resources%20and%20energy%20sources.%20Merino%20Industries%20is%20pursuing%20a%20%E2%80%98Water%20Neutrality%20Goal%E2%80%99%20through%20efficient%20water%20management%20practices%2C%20striving%20to%20reduce%20emissions%2C%20and%20implementing%20measures%20to%20improve%20air%20quality%20while%20minimising%20greenhouse%20gas%20(GHG)%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lohia%20notes%20that%20while%20any%20industry%20would%20attempt%20to%20maximise%20production%20in%20additional%20land%20available%2C%20at%20Merino%2C%20green%20practices%20have%20always%20been%20the%20priority.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20the%20development%20of%20Miyawaki%20forests%20(multi-layered%20forests%20consisting%20of%20native%20plant%20species)%