0make%20sure%20to%20store%20all%20food%20items%20in%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20with%20proper%20sealing%20to%20prevent%20mould%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20through%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%20is%20nestled%20among%20heritage%20buildings%20from%20the%20British%20era%2C%20including%20St%20Mary%E2%80%99s%20Church%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20a%20museum%20showcasing%20pre-independence%20history.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20in%20a%20hurry%2C%20give%20us%20a%20miss%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20tagline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20truly%20matters%20is%20that%20our%20guests%20experience%20a%20journey%20through%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shipra%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%20She%20proudly%20mentions%20that%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20has%20earned%20TripAdvisor%E2%80%99s%20Traveller%E2%80%99s%20Choice%20Award%20for%20the%20ninth%20year%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20team%20consists%20of%20five%20permanent%20local%20employees%2C%20and%20during%20busy%20times%20like%20the%20monsoon%2C%20the%20couple%20recruits%20extra%20help%20on%20a%20temporary%20basis.%20Its%20guest%20list%20includes%20prominent%20figures%20like%20Anupam%20Kher%2C%20Jackie%20Shroff%2C%20Boman%20Irani%2C%20and%20Major%20General%20GD%20Bakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.52_11zon-1723127224.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20in%20a%20hurry%2C%20give%20us%20a%20miss%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20tagline.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.52_11zon-1723127224.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F