0by%20Pune-based%20urban%20planner%20and%20architect%20Snehal%20Karlekar%20(46)%2C%20architect%20Tushar%20Shetye%20(46)%2C%20social%20worker%20and%20banking%20professional%20Uday%20Jagtap%20(52)%2C%20and%20restauranteur%20Ajit%20Ingawle%20(46)%2C%20reverberates%20with%20echoes%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20today%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20explore%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChavni%20was%20a%20coming%20together%20of%20modern%20ideas%20and%20history%2C%20says%20Karlekar.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20four%20of%20us%20met%20over%20the%20years%20while%20engaged%20in%20different%20projects.%E2%80%9D%20United%20by%20the%20common%20zeal%20to%20improve%20the%20tourism%20scene%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20they%20joined%20hands.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20always%20been%20inclined%20towards%20vernacular%20architecture.%20The%20state%20had%20a%20great%20traditional%20wisdom%20and%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Her%20use%20of%20past%20tense%20is%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20say%20this%20%5Bthe%20culture%5D%20persists.%20Most%20of%20it%20is%20now%20fusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20states.%20Cognisant%20about%20how%20North%20and%20South%20India%20still%20have%20footprints%20of%20their%20cultures%20on%20the%20land%2C%20she%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314658%2Fhow-halwa-dagine-maharashtra-traditional-sugar-jewellery-is-made-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20places%20where%20culture%20is%20fading%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20backed%20by%20an%20intent%20to%20get%20native%20and%20non-native%20Maharashtra%20dwellers%20to%20%E2%80%9Cknow%E2%80%9D%20the%20true%20history%20of%20their%20land%2C%20the%20four%20decided%20to%20dive%20into%20a%20project%20that%20would%20render%20this%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20when%20Karlekar%20opens%20a%20letter%20from%20a%20guest%20who%20expresses%20their%20happiness%20at%20havin