om%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-3-1723091250-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360262%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVikas%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20set%20weekly%20or%20monthly%20targets%20to%20remain%20consistent%20in%20studies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20importance%20of%20keeping%20oneself%20updated%20about%20current%20affairs%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CYour%20first%20task%20of%20the%20day%20should%20be%20to%20study%20current%20affairs%20but%20aspirants%20neglect%20this%20section.%20They%20feel%20reading%20Vision%20365%20magazine%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20would%20be%20helpful.%20But%20you%20need%20to%20follow%20news%20articles%20daily%20and%20remain%20aware%20about%20daily%20happenings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Do%20not%20neglect%20qualifying%20paper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Services%20Aptitude%20Test%20or%20CSAT%20is%20GS%20Paper-2%20in%20the%20preliminary%20examination.%20It%20is%20conducted%20to%20evaluate%20an%20aspirant%E2%80%99s%20comprehension%2C%20logical%20reasoning%2C%20general%20mental%20ability%2C%20and%20basic%20numeracy%20skills.%20As%20it%20is%20a%20qualifying%20paper%20requiring%20a%20minimum%20of%2033%20percent%2C%20Vikas%20says%2C%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20tend%20to%20neglect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20the%20CSAT%20paper%20was%20very%20difficult.%20Most%20of%20the%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20come%20from%20BA%20and%20BSc%20background%20and%20some%20lack%20reasoning%20and%20mathematics%20abilities.%20They%20lose%20their%20confidence%20in%20CSAT.%20Despite%20this%2C%20they%20focus%20on%20other%20subjects%20more.%20Remember%20to%20give%20equal%20weightage%20to%20such%20subjects%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%2C%20Vikas%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20set%20weekly%20or%20monthly%20targets%20to%20remain%20consistent%20in%20studies.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20not%20sleep%20if%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20complete%20my%20targets%20even%20if%20it%20was%203%20in%20the%20night.%20However%2C%20remember%20to%20take%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20break%20sometimes%20to%20feel%20rejuvenated.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20is%20just%20an%20exam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723095244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-2-1723091324.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360088%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IFS%20officer%20Vikas%20Singh%20Meena%20shattered%20several%20stereotypes%20about%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20by%20clearing%20the%20UPSC-CSE%202023%20examination%2C%20with%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20672.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360088%2Fupsc-cse-hindi-medium-aspirants-ifs-officer-vikas-singh-meena-shares-tips-study-material-current-affairs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Turned%20My%20Life%20Around%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20a%20Farmer%20Built%20An%20Aloe%20Vera%20Business%20With%20a%20Turnover%20of%20Rs%203.5%20Cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20drought-prone%20Satara%20district%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20farmers%20were%20largely%20dependent%20on%20rain%20for%20irrigation.%20Often%20without%20any%20regular%20irrigation%20facilities%2C%20they%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20crops%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20two%20decades%20back%2C%20farmers%20in%20Padali%20village%20were%20fooled%20into%20taking%20up%20aloe%20vera%20farming%20by%20claiming%20the%20crop%20would%20ensure%20good%20yield%20in%20the%20rainfed%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20businessman%20had%20come%20to%20our%20village%20and%20advertised%20about%20aloe%20vera%20farming.%20He%20distributed%20pamphlets%20wherein%20farmers%20had%20stacks%20of%20money%20on%20one%20hand%20and%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20on%20the%20other.%20It%20mentioned%20%E2%80%98Aloe%20vera%20%3Cem%3Elagaiye%20aur%20lakho%20kamaiye%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grow%20aloe%20vera%20and%20earn%20in%20lakhs)%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20farmer%20Hrushikesh%20Jayasing%20Dhane%20(44).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfluenced%20by%20this%2C%20several%20farmers%20bought%20thousands%20of%20plants%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F301751%2Fbusiness-school-grad-leaves-london-to-organic-farm-help-farmers-earn-jaivik-jeevan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanted%20them%20on%20their%20barren%20lands%20%3C%2Fa%3Eimagining%20themselves%20as%20the%20man%20in%20the%20advertisement.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20curious%20about%20the%20crop%2C%20but%20I%20also%20had%20doubts%20about%20it.%20So%20I%20went%20to%20the%20office%20and%20enquired%20about%20the%20market.%20I%20asked%20to%20be%20told%20about%2010%20such%20farmers%20who%20earned%20lakhs%20from%20aloe%20vera.%20The%20local%20officials%20got%20angry%20and%20threw%20me%20out%20of%20the%20office%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20harvesting%20period%20came%20in%2C%20Hrushikesh%20says%2C%20the%20businessman%20had%20run%20away.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20all%20a%20fraud.%20I%20saw%20farmers%20crying.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20any%20strategy%20to%20market%20the%20crop%2C%20so%20they%20started%20clearing%20their%20fields%20and%20some%20threw%20them%20on%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20Interestingly%2C%20Hrushikesh%20picked%20the%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20and%20planted%20them%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20took%20him%20on%20a%20path%20which%20led%20him%20to%20establishing%2C%20what%20is%20today%2C%20a%20multi-crore%20company!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20on%20his%20field.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELife%20in%20the%20drought-prone%20village%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20a%20humble%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20Hrushikesh%20owned%20eight%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Padali%20village.%20The%20family%20had%20traditionally%20been%20growing%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20pearl%20millet%2C%20sorghum%2C%20and%20wheat.%20Despite%20toiling%20hard%20on%20the%20field%2C%20they%20would%20not%20get%20sufficient%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20rainwater%20for%20irrigation%2C%20as%20the%20nearest%20river%20was%20four%20kilometres%20away%2C%20and%20we%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20machinery%20for%20lift%20irrigation.%20Consequently%2C%20our%20crops%20often%20dried%20up.%20Despite%20having%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20land%2C%20it%20remained%20barren%20for%20much%20of%20the%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20four%20was%20dependent%20on%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20lived%20in%20a%20small%20%3Cem%3Ekachha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud)%20home.%20Such%20was%20the%20financial%20status%20of%20the%20family%20that%20they%20survived%20on%20low-quality%20sorghum%20%3Cem%3Echapatis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flatbread)%2C%20and%20occasionally%2C%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20Class%2010%2C%20Hrushikesh%20never%20wore%20a%20pair%20of%20slippers.%20At%2020%2C%20to%20supplement%20his%20family%20income%20and%20support%20his%20higher%20education%2C%20he%20started%20working%20for%20a%20marketing%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20job%2C%20I%20would%20receive%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20month%20if%20I%20met%20the%20target%20of%20promoting%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20sales.%20This%20income%20was%20not%20fixed%2C%20and%20they%20required%20me%20to%20relocate%2025%20km%20away.%20I%20attempted%20to%20do%20this%20work%20for%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%20but%20it%20became%20unsustainable%20because%20I%20also%20had%20to%20manage%20my%20field%20responsibilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20says%20farmers%20can%20earn%20good%20profits%20if%20they%20make%20products%20from%20aloe%20vera%20like%20juice%2C%20soaps%2C%20fertilisers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media