hat%20they%20would%20act%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENobody%20did%20anything.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20time%20before%20social%20media%2C%20smartphones%20and%20unlimited%20calling%2C%20Dushyant%20woke%20his%20parents%20up%20in%20a%20panic%2C%20activated%20international%20calling%20on%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20phone%20and%20called%20the%20Miami%20police%20department%E2%80%99s%20emergency%20line.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20fighting%20tears%2C%20I%20tried%20my%20best%20to%20convey%20to%20them%20what%20was%20going%20on%2C%20and%20they%20kept%20transferring%20me%20to%20different%20people%2C%20until%20they%20connected%20me%20to%20someone%20who%20told%20me%20that%20his%20phone%20was%20from%20the%20Broward%20County%20in%20Florida%2C%20and%20that%20I%20should%20contact%20the%20Sheriff%20of%20that%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dushyant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dushyant%2C%20Batman%20of%20Bengaluru%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdushyant1-1723012565-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360081%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDushyant%2C%20Batman%20of%20Bengaluru%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20phone%20had%20run%20out%20of%20balance%2C%20he%20shared%20this%20number%20with%20the%20forum%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20make%20the%20call%20to%20the%20Sheriff.%20Thankfully%2C%20someone%20called%20the%20Sheriff.%20When%20Dushyant%20made%20the%20call%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20from%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20phone%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20told%20that%20the%20police%20officers%20were%20on%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20he%20watched%20on%20the%20live%20stream%20as%20cops%20entered%20and%20covered%20the%20camera.%20Few%20hours%20later%2C%20Abraham%E2%80%99s%20sister%20posted%20on%20the%20forum%20that%20he%20had%20passed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20has%20made%20its%20way%20onto%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3275718%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20internet%20mediations%20and%20good%20samaritans%20where%20the%2017-year-old%20from%20India%20finds%20mention.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20also%20did%20is%20help%20this%20young%20boy%20find%20his%20purpose%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20others.%20His%20intrinsic%20goodness%20and%20splendid%20effort%20to%20help%20a%20stranger%20living%20in%20a%20faraway%20country%20was%20appreciated%20by%20people%20around%20the%20world%2C%20with%20messages%20pouring%20in.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20got%20it%2C%20I%20never%20understood%20why%20what%20I%20did%20deserved%20so%20much%20praise%20and%20commendation.%20I%20just%20did%20what%20anyone%20else%20should%20have%20done%3B%20what%20the%20very%20first%20person%20who%20saw%20that%20post%20should%20have%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dushyant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20incident%20changed%20the%20young%20boy%20completely%2C%20and%20turned%20him%20into%20a%20compassionate%20teenager%20for%20whom%20helping