nID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359739%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Khel%20Ratna%20awardee%20Manika%20Batra%20has%20become%20a%20household%20name%20after%20her%20performance%20at%20Paris%20Olympics.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20table%20tennis%20player's%2015-year-long%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359739%2Fmanika-batra-paris-olympics-2024-table-tennis-first-indian-paddler-pre-quarter-finals-career%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LinkedIn%20For%20Blue%20Collar%20Jobs%3A%20Bihar%20Man%20Built%20India%E2%80%99s%201st%20Job%20Portal%20for%20Daily%20Wage%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJanuary%202020%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20rainy%20day%20in%20Delhi.%20Chandrashekar%20Mandal%20had%20just%20started%20work%20at%20his%20new%20finance%20job%20and%20was%20enjoying%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20from%20the%20balcony%20of%20his%20office%20on%20the%20second%20floor.%20As%20he%20stood%20outside%2C%20the%20glaring%20disparity%20of%20life%20stared%20back%20at%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20he%20was%2C%20away%20from%20the%20harsh%20monsoon%2C%20in%20fact%20enjoying%20it%20as%20a%20corporate%20employee.%20But%20right%20in%20front%20of%20his%20eyes%20were%20hundreds%20of%20people%20fighting%20for%20a%20safe%20space%20to%20shelter%20from%20the%20rains%20in%20a%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowk%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20place%20where%20labourers%20wait%20to%20get%20hired)%20opposite%20his%20office.%20These%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F324237%2Fmaharashtra-sunil-khachakad-bhagwan-topped-mpsc-psi-exam-inspiring-story-police-sub-inspector%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edaily%20wage%20labourers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20waiting%20in%20hopes%20of%20being%20hired%20for%20the%20day%2C%20scrambled%20for%20cover%2C%20be%20it%20under%20a%20tree%20or%20a%20food%20stall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20this%20gave%20Chandrashekhar%20flashbacks%20to%20his%20childhood%20in%20Bihar%2C%20where%20he%20had%20seen%20his%20relatives%20go%20through%20the%20harrowing%20experience%20of%20searching%20for%20daily%20work.%20%E2%80%9CIsn%E2%80%99t%20there%20a%20better%20way%20for%20these%20workers%20to%20find%20jobs%3F%20While%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20going%20digital%2C%20why%20not%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20wondered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20later%2C%20when%20the%20nation%20went%20under%20lockdown%2C%20it%20was%20these%20migrant%20workers%20who%20bore%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20crisis.%20The%20images%20of%20some%20walking%20thousands%20of%20kilometres%20to%20reach%20their%20homes%20still%20haunt%20us%20today.%20Their%20plight%20heightened%20the%2029-year-old%E2%80%99s%20wish%20to%20make%20their%20lives%20better%20by%20providing%20them%20jobs%20online%2C%20which%20would%20accord%20them%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20true%20to%20his%20word%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20started%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20%E2%80%94%20an%20online%20platform%20providing%20jobs%20for%20daily%20wage%20labourers%2C%20rescuing%20them%20from%20a%20life%20of%20waiting%20on%20the%20streets.%20Over%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20the%20company%20has%20provided%20a%20regular%20income%20to%20over%20one%20lakh%20workers%2C%20according%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20this%20boy%20from%20Ami%20village%20in%20Darbhanga%2C%20Bihar%2C%20brought%20change%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20lakhs%20of%20migrant%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20should%20workers%20migrate%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20very%20rural%20part%20of%20Bihar%2C%20in%20a%20village%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302115%2Fdelhi-doctors-and-volunteers-give-free-healthcare-to-poor-people-on-streets-vi