iv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9EWHhrCBDV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%23%F0%9D%9F%8F%20%F0%9D%90%82%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%A7%F0%9D%90%AC%F0%9D%90%AD%F0%9D%90%AB%F0%9D%90%AE%F0%9D%90%9C%F0%9D%90%AD%F0%9D%90%A2%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%A7%20%F0%9D%90%82%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%A6%F0%9D%90%A9%F0%9D%90%9A%F0%9D%90%A7%F0%9D%90%B2%20%7C%20%F0%9D%90%83%F0%9D%90%A2%F0%9D%90%A0%F0%9D%90%A2%F0%9D%90%AD%F0%9D%90%9A%F0%9D%90%A5%20%F0%9D%90%8B%F0%9D%90%9A%F0%9D%90%9B%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%AE%F0%9D%90%AB%20%F0%9D%90%82%F0%9D%90%A1%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%B0%F0%9D%90%A4%20(%40digitallabourchowk)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20months%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20and%20his%20team%20campaigned%20in%20these%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%2020-litre%20thermos%20jars%20filled%20with%20cold%20drinks%20like%20Roohafza.%20If%20it%20was%20winter%2C%20the%20drink%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20spoke%20to%20them%20and%20explained%20what%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20do.%20This%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341766%2Fodisha-daily-wage-labourer-isak-munda-becomes-youtube-star-with-food-videos-watch%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20opportunity%20to%20escape%20a%20life%20of%20uncertainty%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20most%20migrant%20workers%20are%20from%20Bihar%2C%20we%20explained%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20migrate%20all%20the%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chandrashekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20set%20up%20kiosks%20in%20highly%20populated%20districts%20to%20spread%20the%20word.%20To%20get%20contractors%2C%20project%20managers%20and%20companies%20on%20board%2C%20they%20partnered%20with%20builders%E2%80%99%20associations%20and%20Real%20Estate%20Regulatory%20Authority%20(RERA)%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Noida.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20joined%20over%20100%20construction%20groups%20on%20Facebook%20to%20build%20contacts%20and%20find%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20is%20built%20for%20construction%20companies%20and%20workers%2C%20masons%2C%20painters%2C%20carpenters%2C%20etc.%20When%20a%20customer%20(contractor)%20signs%20up%2C%20they%20add%20details%20like%20location%2C%20kind%20of%20job%2C%20wages%20per%20day%2C%20number%20of%20days%20for%20which%20labour%20is%20required%2C%20and%20whether%20accommodation%20and%20food%20are%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20can%20access%20these%20details%20and%20call%20the%20job%20poster%20directly%20to%20express%20their%20interest.%20On%20the%20workers%E2%80%99%20side%2C%20they%20add%20details%20like%20their%20skills%2C%20past%20experiences%2C%20and%20minimum%20wages.%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20is%20working%20to%20make%20digital%20labour%20cards%20for%20these%20workers%2C%20which%20will%20provide%20them%20with%20an%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20planning%20to%20give%20incentives%20based%20on%20their%20performance%20to%20boost%20their%20morale.%20This%20is%20our%20effort%20to%20organise%20the%20informal%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Noida%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomers%20get%2010%20connections%20for%20free%2C%20post%20which%20they%20pay%20a%20subscription%20fee.%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20is%20free%20for%20workers.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20in%20the%20process%20of%20partnering%20with%20institutes%20to%20provide%20upskilling%20courses%20for%20the%20workers%2C%20as%20there%20is%20a%20dearth%20of%20skilled%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShrawan%20Kumar%20from%20Darbhanga%20has%20been%20free%20of%20worry%20for%20the%20past%20year.%20He%20was%20employed%20by%20a%20builder%20in%20Jodhpur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20on%20a%20long-term%20contract.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20earned%20in%20one%20year%20what%20I%20used%20to%20earn%20in%20three%20years.%20We%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20stand%20in%20the%20heat%20daily%20looking%20for%20jobs.%20When%20one%20contract%20is%20about%20to%20end%2C%20we%20can%20choose%20the%20next%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20projects%20last%20for%20at%20least%2021%20days%2C%20according%20to%20Chandrashekhar.%20He%20claims%20that%20there%20are%20500%20to%201%2C000%20jobs%20posted%20daily%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzhar%20Ansari%2C%20who%20runs%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh-based%20construction%20company%2C%20explains%20that%20they%20are%20always%20short%20of%20manpower.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20hire%20workers%20as%20we%20fall%20short.%20We%20just%20put%20in%20our%20criteria%20on%20the%20app%20and%20we%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20workers%20according%20to%20the%20requirements%20from%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20good%20effort%20and%20makes%20the%20hiring%20process%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognised%20by%20Startup%20Bihar%2C%20Startup%20India%2C%20Citibank%2C%20and%20more%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20is%20rearing%20to%20go.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20provide%20a%20credible%20virtual%20identity%20for%20these%20workers.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20transform%20this%20unorganised%2C%20unidentified%20sector%2C%20and%20provide%20them%20visibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumit%20Kumar%20agrees%2C%20as%20he%20no%20longer%20has%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20his%20family%20for%20months%2C%20now%20that%20he%20can%20find%20options%20nearby!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Chandrashekar%20Mandal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722845966000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk1-